OL,3,CDouble child-murderer and rapist
OL,4,Ccannot be released from prison
OL,6,FDouble-child murderer and rapist Colin
OL,7,FPitchfork will not be released from
OL,8,Fprison after serving his minimum
OL,9,Fsentence, the Parole Board has ruled.
OL,11,FPitchfork was jailed for life in 1988
OL,12,Fafter raping and strangling 15-year-
OL,13,Folds Lynda Mann and Dawn Ashworth in
OL,14,FLeicestershire in 1983 and 1986.
OL,16,FHe was 27 when he became the first man
OL,17,Fto be convicted in the UK using DNA
OL,18,Fprofiling. He was sentenced to a
OL,19,Fminimum term of 28 years, which has
OL,20,Fnow passed.
