OL,3,CDouble child-murderer and rapist
OL,4,Ccannot be released from prison
OL,6,FBut the killer will stay behind bars
OL,7,Fas the Parole Board announced on
OL,8,FThursday it denied his release. He has
OL,9,F21 days to apply for reconsideration.
OL,11,FIt said in a decision summary: "After
OL,12,Fconsidering the circumstances of his
OL,13,Foffending, the progress made while in
OL,15,Fcustody, and on licence, and the
OL,16,Fevidence presented at the hearing, the
OL,17,Fpanel was not satisfied that release
OL,18,Fat this point would be safe for the
OL,19,Fprotection of the public.
