OL,6,Fconsistent with placement in an open
OL,7,Fprison."
OL,9,FSouth Leicestershire MP Alberto Costa
OL,10,Fsaid he was "reassured" by the board's
OL,11,Fdeision.
OL,13,FHe said: "I am relieved by the Parole
OL,14,FBoard's decision to keep brutal double
OL,15,Fchild rapist and killer behind bars
OL,16,Fwhere he belongs.
OL,18,F"This news will bring some reassurance
OL,19,Fto the families of Lynda and Dawn and
OL,20,Fto the wider public.
