OL,6,F"At 65 years old, he still has decades
OL,7,Fof life ahead of him and the capacity
OL,8,Fto pose a real risk to the public,
OL,9,Fthat is why I welcome the Parole
OL,10,FBoard's decision today.
OL,12,F"Their job is to assess risk, and it
OL,13,Fis obvious to me that the world is a
OL,14,Ffar more dangerous place if Pitchfork
OL,15,Fis released."
