OL,6,FPitchfork previously convinced the
OL,7,FParole Board to release him in 2021,
OL,8,Fbut he was soon back behind bars after
OL,9,Fbreaching conditions when he
OL,10,Fapproached a lone woman while litter
OL,11,Fpicking.
OL,13,FThe Parole Board then found in June
OL,14,F2023 that the decision to recall him
OL,15,Fto prison was flawed and that his
OL,16,Fdetention was no longer necessary for
OL,17,Fpublic safety.
