OL,6,FBut this ruling was blocked by then-
OL,7,FJustice Secretary Alex Chalk as he
OL,8,Fcalled for the decision to release
OL,9,FPitchfork to be reviewed, which kept
OL,10,Fhim behind bars.
OL,12,FLast year he was due to face a fresh
OL,13,Fhearing over whether he should be
OL,14,Freleased again, but this was postponed
OL,15,Fafter he launched a legal challenge
OL,16,Fover the extent of material he has
OL,17,Fbeen allowed to see related to "fresh
OL,18,Fallegations" about his behaviour in
OL,19,Fprison.
